title: UP TO 12% off
description:
* Sales period: 6 January - 31 March 2023.
* Travel period: 6 January - 31 August 2023.
* To redeem the offer, all you need to do is enter the promotional code UBL2023 when booking your flight on www.qatarairways.com/ubloffer and make the payment with your UBL card.
* For travel originating from Pakistan.
* Offer valid on Qatar Airways operated flights only (not applicable on any interline or codeshare flights).
* Discount applies to the base airfare fare only.
* Discount does not apply to taxes, surcharges and all other standard market surcharges.
* Offer is applicable to select online destinations: JFK, IAH, IAD, SFO, ATL, DFW, BOS, ORD, SEA, LAX, MIA, PHL, YUL, YYZ, LHR, MAN, LGW, IST, SAW, ESB, AYT, BJV, ADA, CDG, BCN, FRA, DUS, AGP, MXP, CPH, AMS, TXL, ARN, FCO, VCE, ZRH, GVA, MAD, BUD, DUB, MUC, OSL, HEL, BRU, PRG, WAW, MLE, SIN, KUL, HKT, BKK, MNL, CEB, CRK, DPS, CGK, SYD, MEL, PER, BNE, SEZ, NBO, ZNZ, CBR, GYD, MED, DMM.
* Qatar Airways will not be responsible for any fare differences if customers fail to enter the given promo code at the time of booking.
* Fares displayed will already include the applicable discounts.
* Flights eligible for the discount are clearly signaled with a sales tag beside them. Please ensure only flights eligible for the discount are selected when booking.
* Customers who did not receive a discount, cannot be credited retrospectively.
* Valid for return and one-way fares only.
* 12% discount on base fare amount in Business Class will apply to booking classes: D, I.
* 10% discount on base fare amount in Business Class will apply to booking classes: R.
* 12% discount on base fare amount in Economy Class will apply to booking classes: S, V, L, M, K.
* 10% discount on base fare amount in Economy Class will apply to booking classes: N, O, T, Q.
* The following booking classes are excluded from this offer: Y, B, H, J, P, C, A, F.
* This offer may be used more than once during the offer period.
* Not valid in combination with any other promotion or any other market fares.
* Changes and Cancellation: see detailed fare rules at the time of booking.
* Seats are limited and might not be available on all flights; subject to availability in the respective booking class at the time of booking.
* Minimum Stay / Maximum Stay depends on the class booked. Please review at the time of booking.
* For full terms and conditions, please review detailed fare rules at the time of booking.

title: UP TO 10% off on Treatments
description:
* Get up to 10% discount for treatments with the best medical experts, hospitals & clinics.
* Redemption Method: On-spot Discount
  * Step 1: Go to www.vaidam.com/mastercard-offers
  * Step 2: Fill up the enquiry form-Name, Email, Contact Number, Country, A brief about the medical issue
  * Step 3 : Within 24 hours of receiving the enquiry, Vaidamassigns a case manager for the patient
  * Step 4: Case manager connects with the patient via email/ phone/ WhatsApp and collects more details 
  * Step 5: Case manager connects with doctors and hospitals in the preferred destination of the patient and prepare a treatment plan including the cost of treatment. 
  * Step 6 : Case manager helps patient with other documentation that patient may need to travel -for eg-appointment letter, visa invitation letter, letter for employer etc.
  * Step 6: Patient then books their flight to the destination country and share the itinerary with the case manager. Case manager then makes further arrangements for airport transfer, hotel reservation -depending on the patient preference.
  * Step 7: The case manager informs the hospital before the patient arrival that the patient is eligible for special discount for Mastercard holders.
  * Step 8: Patient starts the treatment at the hospital and at the time of discharge from the hospital, the discount is applied
* Exclusions/Inclusions/Subjectivity:
  * Discount applied on the treatment cost is uncapped.
  * 10% discount on Service fees for Cardholders inTurkeyand India
  * 5% discount on Service fees UAE region.
  * Existing patients of a hospital will NOT be eligible for this discount.
  * Patients using services of any other medical facilitator agency for hospital logistics shall NOT be eligible for the discount.
  * Certain treatments where cost > USD 20,000 OR treatment which involves implants with value >USD 10,000 may NOT be eligible for the flat discounts. Patient will have to check with the case manager for the applicability of discount for such treatments
* Mastercard® is not a licensed provider of any medical services and does not sell, solicit, or provide advice on health services,medical procedures or products. Mastercard expressly states that Mastercard shall not beliable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, special, or other damages arising from or related to, your use of the services referred to herein or any other service you may access pursuant to this promotion, regardless of whether you knew or should have known of the possibility of such damages. You acknowledge and agree that Mastercard does not recommend and/or endorse any specific physicians, products, procedures, opinions or other services that may be mentioned or accessible on this site. You further acknowledge and agree that you access such medical services, products and procedures solely at your own risk and option.

title: 15% off
description:
* As a Visa cardholder, enjoy 15% discount at 100+ IHG Hotels & Resorts across Middle East and Africa.
* The Visa promotional rate (the “Promotion”) is valid only for bookings made from 05 October 2022 through 31 March 2023 (both dates inclusive) (“Booking Dates”) for stays at participating hotels between 08 October 2022 to 03 April 2023 
(both dates inclusive) (“Stay Dates”) using the “Visa IMEA Partner Rate”.
* Booking must be made via the dedicated offer landing page in order to redeem the discount.
* English - https://www.ihg.com/content/gb/en/deals/partner-offers/visa-mea?qCpid=787067559&srb_u=1&cm_mmc=WEB-_-6C-_-IMEA-_-QE-_-PTR-_-VISAMEA2022_1017100-_-vanity
* Arabic - https://www.ihg.com/content/ae/ar/deals/partner-offers/visa-mea?qCpid=787067559&srb_u=1&cm_mmc=WEB-_-6C-_-IMEA-_-AR-_-PTR-_-VISAMEA2022_1017100-_-vanity
* The Promotion offers a minimum discount of 15% off the hotel’s Best Flexible Rate (BFR).
* Minimum 1 night stay required.
* Stay must include Thursday, Friday, Saturday or Sunday night as part of the booking.
* Booking must be made at least three (3) days in advance.
* Cancellation and no-show policy apply. Booking can be cancelled 72 hours before check in time without any charge.
* No shows or cancellations made less than 72 hours before your check in time will result in a charge of full stay.
* Rates are per room, per night based on a maximum of 2 adults sharing a standard twin/double room and are subject to availability.
* This offer is only available to Visa card holders via official Visa partner channels. Bookings must be made through the dedicated offer landing page and must be booked and paid for using a Visa card.
* The Promotion offer is valid in IHG Middle East & Africa properties across Angola, Algeria, Bahrain, Egypt, Ghana, Jordan, Kenya, Kuwait, Lebanon, Mauritius, Oman, Qatar, Saudi Arabia, South Africa, Tanzania, United Arab Emirates, 
Zambia and Zimbabwe at participating InterContinental, voco, Crowne Plaza, Hotel Indigo, Holiday Inn, Holiday Inn Express and Staybridge Suites hotels and resorts. See dedicated landing page for full details of participating hotels.
* The Promotion offer is not valid in conjunction with any other offer, discount or promotion.
* Kids up to 12 years and sharing the room with full paying adults eat free with an accompanying paying adult guest at the hotel restaurant. Bookings made through IHG Brand websites, IHG App, CRO or directly at hotel qualify for IHG One 
Rewards Points. Standard IHG One Rewards program terms and conditions apply. Visit ihgonerewards.com for details.
* IHG reserves the right to remove a member’s points or cancel a member’s account if fraudulent use of the Promotion is detected.
* Tax, service charge, credit card surcharges are not included.
* Any other in-room dining purchases, minibar purchases and private dining are excluded from this offer.
* Visa card (all Visa cards applicable excluding Prepaid) guarantee is required to make a booking.
* The Promotion is not applicable to group bookings.
* Unused components do not have a cash value and are non-refundable.
* Not applicable with other discounted rate promotions.
* Blackout dates (days when the offers are not available) may apply in some participating hotels.
* IHG reserves the right to withdraw, suspend or modify this Promotion or amend these terms and conditions without prior notice at any time with or without notice and without any liability.
* To the extent permitted by applicable law, IHG reserves the right of final interpretation of this Promotion.
* Final bill will be in hotel’s local currency.
* Eligible countries: The Visa Promotion is limited to Visa Credit and Visa Debit cards issued in Afghanistan, Algeria, Angola, Bahrain, Benin, Botswana, Burkina Faso, Burundi, Cameroon, Cape Verde Islands, Chad, Comoros, Congo, Cote D' 
Ivoire, Democratic Republic Congo, Djibouti, Egypt, Equatorial Guinea, Eritrea, Ethiopia, Gabon, Gambia, Ghana, Guinea, Guinea Bissau, Iran, Iraq, Jordan, Kenya, Kuwait, Lebanon, Lesotho, Liberia, Libya, Madagascar, Malawi, Mali, 
Mauritania, Mauritius, Morocco, Mozambique, Namibia, Niger, Nigeria, Oman, Pakistan, Palestine, Qatar, Rwanda, Sao Tome and Principe, Saudi Arabia, Senegal, Seychelles, Sierra Leone, Somalia, South Africa, South Sudan, Sudan, 
Swaziland, Syria, Tanzania, Togo, Tunisia, United Arab Emirates, Uganda, Western Sahara, Yemen Arab Republic, Zambia and Zimbabwe.

title: UP TO 10% Cashback
description:
* To avail of the promo offer,visit www.booking.com/10visacemea
* (the“OfferLandingPage”) and proceed with the following steps:
  * Signup or login to a registered Booking.com account.
  * Search for the accommodation and travel dates. Only properties labelled with a‘cashback badge’are eligible.
  * Choose the preferred accommodation and room type to see the rate and estimated cashback value.
  * Use an eligible Visa Card (excluding Visa non-reloadable prepaid cards) to complete the booking.
  * Tick the check box on Payment Page to enable cash back to the eligible Visa Card.
  * Use an eligible Visa Card (excluding Visa non-reloadable prepaid cards) to pay at the accommodation.
  * Taxes and other fees and charges may not be taken in to account for the calculation of the final cashback.The final cash back is subject to the exchange rate.
  * The cash back will be credited at least 64 business days after completion of stay in the accommodation to the Cardholder’s Visa Card.
  * Accommodations that do not accept credit cards are not eligible for the offer.
  * The offer is subject to terms and conditions of Booking.com. In case of dispute, the decision of Booking.com and Visa shall be final.
  * All conditions of the promotion must be met at the time the booking is made; retro active claims are not allowed.
  * Cash back will be granted only to the user who made the booking and completed their stay.
  * These terms are to be read together with the complete conditions of use here and here and any other terms that apply to your trip.In the event of an inconsistency or discrepancy about the contents of these summarized conditions of use then the complete conditions of use, to the extent permitted by law, shall apply, prevail, and be conclusive.
  * For inquiries and concerns about the offer, you may call Booking.com Customer Service at: https://www.booking.com/content/contact-us.html
* Terms & Conditions apply.

title: Enjoy 20% Off on 3 Rides Every Month
description:
* You can use you Askari Mastercard Credit Cards on Careem app and get 20% off 3 rides every month 
* You can avail the offer by using ‘MASTERCARD' ” into the Promo Code tab on the checkout screen
* You can avail the offer using your Askari Gold, Platinum and World Mastercard Credit Cards
* The offer is valid until 30 June 2023
* You can avail a maximum discount of 20% or USD 11 (in equivalent local Currency i.e. PKR)
* The discount is available on all car types, except Hala Taxi
* The promotion is not applicable when you pay with Apple Pay
* Offer valid for rides paid with Askari Mastercard Credit Cards
* You rides cannot be accumulated
* The discounts are not valid in conjunction with other special promotions, discounts programs or vouchers defined by Askari Bank or alliance partner
* This discounts cannot be combined with group discounts, parties, special events or any other offers (where applicable)
* The partners reserve the right to refuse or cancel any order for any unforeseen reason at any given time
* Askari Bank’s Credit Card members are entitled to discounts in respect to payments made at the alliance partners through their Askari Cards only and discount is not applicable on cash transaction
* Askari Bank shall not be responsible for any customer or third party for unsatisfactory or delayed performance of the partners, losses, damages, delays or cancellation by partners 
* Askari Bank will not be responsible for any complaint or liability whatsoever that arises with respect to items and services availed at the mentioned partner(s)
* Askari Bank and the Alliance Partner reserve the right to amend, terminate, withdraw or change the criteria of any discount offering without providing prior notice or reason
* Askari Bank is not liable for the accuracy of the brand offers mentioned under alliances and for updated brand offers, please refer to the relevant alliance partner’s website
* Askari MasterCard Credit Card Terms and Conditions apply
* Careem Terms &Conditions apply
* How to avail discount
* Step 1: Download or open the Careem app
* Step 2: Click the top right corner of the app, select wallet, add your Askari Mastercard Credit Card required details
* Step 3: Add the promo code "MASTERCARD" into the promo code tab on the checkout screen & enjoy your rides

title: Book Your Stay at Boutique Hotel Taskonaklar with a Complimentary Experience
description:
* Choose one of three complimentary excursions when you book a stay at Taskonaklar Hotel, Cappadocia
* Stay at the Taskonaklar Hotel in Cappadocia and receive a complimentary excursion. You'll get to choose one of three immersive activities: a guided walk through Cappadocia's picturesque valley and a picnic with tea, coffee, cake, pastry, seasonal fruits, local cheeses, dried fruits, and more; a pottery workshop in the scenic hotel garden or your room's private balcony; or a seasonal jam-making workshop or cooking class after a guided valley walk. Exclusively for Mastercard cardholders.
* The first 15 Mastercard Priceless members and their family or friends staying with them within the same reservation will enjoy one of the three exclusive experiences, namely the pottery workshop, a guided valley walk followed by a jam making workshop or a cooking class depending on the season and a valley picnic after a private walking tour.
* The offer is valid until 31.12.2022 and subject to availability at the time of booking.
* The offer is valid for over 18 years old. Guests under the age of 18 can only stay with their families.
* After you enroll for this experience, you will get an e-mail from Priceless including your unique promotion code and the link that will land you to contact page of the Taskonaklar Hotel, Cappadocia. Once you receive all the information, you have 2 weeks to make a reservation for Taskonaklar Hotel, Cappadocia.
* You have to contact the hotel directly via info@taskonaklar.com to finalize your reservation and quote your unique code to redeem one of the three complimentary experiences that are exclusively created for Mastercard cardholders. Depending on the date of your stay, you can also arrange the date and the time for the experience that they chose via the same contact information. Reservations without the unique code will not be valid.
* It is available for the following types of rooms: Junior Suite, One room Suite, Family Suite, Suite with Terrace, Royal Suite with outdoor Hot tub, Queen Suite with outdoor Hot tub, King Suite with outdoor Hot tub

title: Pottery Workshop
description:
* Get hands-on for a pottery workshop in the garden of the Taskonaklar Hotel in Cappadocia
* Try your hand at Cappadocia's most popular craft in a two-hour pottery workshop at the Taskonaklar Hotel. You and your guest will discover the ancient art of pottery with a master potter in the garden of the gorgeous cave hotel. While you work, you'll take in awe-inspiring views of Güvercinlik and the fairy chimneys that make the region's landscape such a marvelous sight.
* The offer is valid until 31.12.2022 and subject to availability at the time of booking.
* The offer is valid for over 18 years old. Guests under the age of 18 can only experience it with their families.
* To make a reservation, you need to contact Taskonaklar Hotel, Cappadocia directly via info@taskonaklar.com
* After purchasing the experience, you have two weeks to complete your reservation.
* You do not have to be a guest of the hotel to buy this experience.
* Price listed is for 1 to 2 people. The maximum amount of people for this experience is 8 and each additional person costs 50 TL.

title: Valley Walk and Jam Making
description:
* Take an enchanting valley walk and a jam-making workshop at the Taskonaklar Hotel in Cappadocia
* Take an exhilarating valley walk and pick fruits for a jam-making workshop at Cappadocia's Taskonaklar Hotel. You'll see the majestic fairy chimneys that make up the region's awe-inspiring landscape, picking fruits like apples, red plums, and apricots if they're in season. Then, you'll take your harvest to the hotel for a jam-making workshop, or, if it's during the off-season, you'll grab ingredients at the farmers' market for a gourmet cooking class in a village house
* Number of people: 2-6 people
* The offer is valid until 31.12.2022 and subject to availability at the time of booking.
* The offer is valid for over 18 years old. Guests under the age of 18 can only experience it with their families.

* After purchasing the experience, you have two weeks to complete your reservation.
* You do not have to be a guest of the hotel to buy this experience.
* Price listed is for 1 to 2 people
* Maximum amount of people for this experience is 6 and each additional person costs 100 TL.

title: Valley Walk and Picnic
description:
* Walk among the fairy chimneys and share a picnic in Turkey’s Cappadocia valley
* Escape your everyday routine with a walking tour and picnic for two in the otherwordly Cappadocia valley. Starting near the Taskonaklar Hotel, you'll embark on a private expedition among the area's famous fairy chimneys. Get up close to the formations as you explore the natural beauty of the region, then gather around a fire pit to enjoy grilled sucuk. You'll also sample a selection of fresh cakes, brioche pastries, dried and seasonal fruits, crackers, and local cheeses. Round out your meal with brewed tea and coffee.
* Number of people: 2-12 people
* The offer is valid until 31.12.2022 and subject to availability at the time of booking.
* The offer is valid for over 18 years old. Guests under the age of 18 can only experience it with their families.

* After purchasing the experience, you have two weeks to complete your reservation.

title: Stay at the Taskonaklar Hotel in Cappadocia & Receive a Complimentary Excursion
description:
* Stay at the Taskonaklar Hotel in Cappadocia and receive a complimentary excursion. You'll get to choose one of three immersive activities: a guided walk through Cappadocia's picturesque valley and a picnic with tea, coffee, cake, pastry, seasonal fruits, local cheeses, dried fruits, and more; a pottery workshop in the scenic hotel garden or your room's private balcony; or a seasonal jam-making workshop or cooking class after a guided valley walk. Exclusively for Mastercard cardholders
* The offer is valid for 18+ years old. Guests under the age of 18 can avail this offer with their families.
* The offer is valid until 31 December 2022 and subject to availability at the time of booking
* Experience is available to the first 15 reservations
* All guests within a single reservation will be able to benefit from the free experience; however, they cannot choose different experiences individually
* The offers are available for the following types of rooms: Junior Suite, One-room Suite, Family Suite, Suite with terrace, Royal Suite with outdoor hot tub, Queen Suite with outdoor hot tub, King Suite with outdoor hot tub
* After registration, you will get an e-mail from Priceless including your unique promotion code and the link that will land you to contact page of the Taskonaklar Hotel, Cappadocia. Once you receive all the information, you have 2 weeks to make a reservation for Taskonaklar Hotel, Cappadocia.
* You have to contact the hotel directly via info@taskonaklar.com to finalize your reservation and quote your unique code to redeem one of the three complimentary experiences that are exclusively created for Mastercard cardholders. Reservations without the unique code will not be valid

title: Private Guided Tour
description:
* Marvel at Cappadocia's most iconic sites on a private guided tour for up to four people. Starting and ending at the Taskonaklar Hotel, you'll embark on a customizable adventure through Turkish history with an expert local guide and private car transportation. See the mysterious fairy chimneys and ancient-civilization ruins that make the landscape so iconic, plus get special access to an ongoing archaeological excavation—a treat not available to the general public. Exclusively for Mastercard cardholders.
* The offer is valid until 31 December 2022 and subject to availability at the time of booking
* The offer is valid for 18+ years old. Guests under the age of 18 can avail this offer with their families.
* To make a reservation, you need to contact Taskonaklar Hotel, Cappadocia directly via info@taskonaklar.com
* After purchasing the experience, you have two weeks to complete your reservation
* Prices listed are for a group of 1 to 4 people and a group of 5 to 12 people . The price is listed on https://www.priceless.com/travel/product/175350/private-guided-tour-taskonaklar-hotel-cappadocia
* The listed price includes a 1-day group tour
* The price includes a professional guide, private vehicle and driver, a custom-made tour, and a priceless addition to the existing tour options, which is an exclusive visit to the ongoing archaeological excavations in the region with an expert guide by obtaining special permission. However, lunch and museum entrance fees are not included in the listed price

title: Sunrise Breakfast
description:
* Witness the sun rising over Turkey's Cappadocia region as you feast on a delectable Turkish breakfast. You and your guest will first jump into a Land Rover Defender and travel into the valley, where you'll sit down to a breakfast prepared by chefs from the Taskonaklar Hotel. You'll gaze over Cappadocia's famous rock formations and the multicolored hot air balloons rising in the air as you are served with a traditional Turkish breakfast offering rich variety of delicacies.
* The offer is valid until 31 December 2022 and subject to availability at the time of booking

title: 20% off on 3 Rides
description:
* Use your Mastercard on Careem App to save 20% on 3 rides every month.
* Download or open the Careem app. After you’ve selected your ride, enter code ”MASTERCARD” into the Promo Code tab on the checkout screen.
* Use an eligible Mastercard as your payment method
* The promotion is not applicable when you pay with Apple Pay.
* The discount is available on all car types, except Hala Taxi. 
* Save 20% on 3 rides every month. Max value per ride is USD 11 or local equivalents PKR 2013.11
* Discount is applicable when successful payment made through BOP MasterCard Debit & Credit Card.
* Discount will not be allowed on applicable Govt. taxes (like GST etc.)
* Offer is not valid in conjunction with any other promotions or discount program.
* BOP or Merchant reserves the right to discontinue or amend any promotional Discount deal at any time.
* For any further information, please call 111 - 267 - 200 or visit http://www.bop.com.pk/CardDiscounts.aspx
